He is Valhalla's finest deity and motivational speaker, Thor.

00:59:02.820 --> 00:59:04.620
Hi. Hello, Amy.

00:59:04.820 --> 00:59:05.620
I'm happy to be here.

00:59:05.820 --> 00:59:07.620
It's been a long journey.

00:59:07.820 --> 00:59:08.620
Uh, yeah.

00:59:08.820 --> 00:59:10.620
