00:59:10.820 --> 00:59:12.620
I mean, I read Beowulf.

00:59:12.820 --> 00:59:13.620
Well, I didn't.

00:59:13.820 --> 00:59:14.620
But I read the cover.

00:59:14.820 --> 00:59:16.620
But, like, you're a Viking, right?

00:59:16.820 --> 00:59:19.620
