You enslave his children, set his house on fire.

01:02:30.420 --> 01:02:32.220
He shall not bother you again.

01:02:32.420 --> 01:02:34.220
It must be nice to have you as a neighbor, not...

01:02:34.420 --> 01:02:37.220
I live in no place longer than needed to fulfill my goals,

01:02:37.420 --> 01:02:39.220
taking slaves, valuables, and food.

01:02:39.420 --> 01:02:42.220
Goal setting is very important, Amy, not just in football.

01:02:42.420 --> 01:02:44.220
You're very weird and creeping me out a bit,

01:02:44.420 --> 01:02:47.220
