01:02:47.420 --> 01:02:49.220
So, what do you think of my city?

01:02:49.420 --> 01:02:51.220
Ah, I like it very much.

01:02:51.420 --> 01:02:53.220
Your women here are prepared for battle.

01:02:53.420 --> 01:02:57.220
