01:02:57.220 --> 01:03:00.020
A woman who wheats well provides for her man.

01:03:00.220 --> 01:03:03.020
You cannot set sail for robbing and pillaging on an empty stomach.

01:03:03.220 --> 01:03:06.020
It's like the story of the parson's wife and the troll.

01:03:06.220 --> 01:03:08.020
