01:05:43.820 --> 01:05:46.620
Thar is never shy. Thar is mighty. Thar is a god.

01:05:46.820 --> 01:05:48.620
And where are you from?

01:05:48.820 --> 01:05:51.620
From the beginning of the flat earth, where the sun meets the sky.

01:05:51.820 --> 01:05:53.620
Oh, right. By the beach. Great.

